column5: Heading to Sturgeon for a couple days - Tomorrow, and Sunday.  The weather seems likes it's gonna be pretty terrible, but we're up for it.  Anyone else gonna be there?
Not going to be there but good luck.  Watch out for lightning.
Thanks.  None in the forecast...yet lol.
Just got back and did pretty well using koppers smelt baits. Try around shoals between 6' and 15'.
